s%2Fmultiagent-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill%20proliferate%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgents%20are%20the%20next%20level%20of%20understanding%20around%20how%20you%20apply%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Jim%20Rowan%2C%20the%20head%20of%20AI%20at%20the%20consultancy%20Deloitte%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20perform%20actions%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FDeloitte%2Fus%2FDocuments%2Fconsulting%2Fus-state-of-gen-ai-q4.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20Deloitte%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%202%2C773%20business%20leaders%2C%2026%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20their%20organizations%20were%20exploring%20autonomous%20agents%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Blarge%20or%20very%20large%20extent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9f8536f-ef7e-4dbe-87f8-4ed5a265afcb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20AI%20agents%20have%20become%20the%20new%20focus%20for%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20the%20generative-AI%20boom%20%E2%80%94%20which%20kicked%20off%20after%20the%20debut%20of%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20late%202022%20%E2%80%94%20most%20businesses%20that%20adopted%20the%20technology%20scaled%20it%20to%20power%20chatbots%20and%20complete%20routine%20tasks%20like%20drafting%20meeting%20summaries.%20AI%20agents%20represent%20an%20evolution%20of%20generative-AI%20technology%2C%20built%20to%20complete%20tasks%20autonomously%2C%20though%20most%20are%20still%20monitored%20closely%20by%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgentic%20AI%20%26quot%3Bactually%20possesses%20some%20unique%20skills%20around%20reasoning%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20orchestration%2C%26quot%3B%20Bedi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThese%20agents%20can%20collaborate%20with%20each%20other%20and%20really%20start%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20work%20happening%20autonomously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuzz%20for%20AI%20agents%20kicked%20into%20high%20gear%20after%20Salesforce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ceo-marc-benioff-says-new-focus-on-ai-agents-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edebuted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Agentforce%20in%20September%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-agentforce-ai-tool-automate-tasks-boost-productivity-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautomate%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20customer%20support%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20marketing.%20The%20company%20has%20said%20it%20will%20roll%20out%201%20billion%20agents%20to%20customers%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20company%20also%20reported%20that%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.salesforce.com%2Fs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E340%2C000%20of%20its%20customer%20support%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20answered%20autonomously%20with%20Agentforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServiceNow%20estimates%20that%20the%20company's%20AI%20agents%2C%20already%20deployed%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20business%2C%20such%20as%20customer%20service%2C%20human%20resources%2C%20and%20IT%2C%20are%20driving%20an%20estimated%20%24325%20million%20in%20annualized%20value%20by%20bolstering%20workplace%20productivity%20by%2020%25.%20ServiceNow%20says%20AI-agent-supported%20work%20saves%20400%2C000%20labor%20hours%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20technology%20companies%20are%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20their%20agentic-AI%20development.%20Many%20are%20figuring%20out%20which%20processes%20they%20can%20fully%20automate%20with%20the%20technology.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20company%20leaders%20implementing%20agentic%20AI%20are%20training%20their%20workers%20to%20collaborate%20with%20%E2%80%94%20and%20provide%20feedback%20on%20%E2%80%94%20their%20new%20%26quot%3Bcoworkers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208cb1fda-cde5-4717-b87a-0f82d5d0e2cd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20agents%20are%20often%20developed%20as%20worker-collaboration%20tools%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Kucera%2C%20the%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20management%20at%20Salesforce%2C%20recommended%20that%20businesses%20be%20transparent%20about%20what%20work%20AI%20agents%20can%20handle%20and%20what%20will%20remain%20with%20workers.%20He%20added%20that%20businesses%20should%20be%20clear%20about%20what%20an%20AI%20agent%20actually%20is%2C%20saying%20that%20not%20all%20agentic%20systems%20are%20equal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20false%20agents%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Kucera%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20an%20agent%20when%20you're%20taking%20a%20request%20and%20the%20agent%20is%20figuring%20out%20what%20to%20do%20and%20then%20what%20data%20to%20put%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20surveys%20frequently%20find%20that%20many%20workers%20worry%20that%20AI%20will%20replace%20them%2C%20technologists%20say%20AI%20agents%20won't%20replace%20people%20but%20assume%20responsibility%20for%20mundane%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20agents%20are%20going%20to%20help%20me%20do%20my%20job%2C%20but%20at%20no%20point%20will%20they%20make%20me%20do%20something%20I'm%20not%20aware%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Walter%20Sun%2C%20the%20global%20head%20of%20AI%20at%20SAP%2C%20which%20sells%20software%20for%20financial%2C%20supply%20chain%2C%20and%20other%20business%20management%20needs.%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20the%20employees%20are%20always%20in%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e64fe235-049a-4d60-8c18-3ef213252b2a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20companies%20are%20tailoring%20AI%20agents%20with%20employee%20feedback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20workers%20have%20a%20voice%20in%20how%20AI%20agents%20are%20developed%2C%20SAP%20encourages%20employees%20across%20its%20various%20business%20lines%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20travel-%20and%20expense-management%20provider%20Concur%20and%20SuccessFactors%2C%20which%20provides%20HR%2C%20payroll%2C%20and%20talent%20management%20software%20%E2%80%94%20to%20use%20an%20internal%20online%20form%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20AI%20team%20and%20propose%20compelling%20agentic%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Intuit%2C%20the%20AI-powered%20financial%20assistant%20Intuit%20Assist%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fquickbooks.intuit.com%2Fr%2Finnovation%2Fintuit-assist-for-quickbooks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20businesses%20paid%2045%25%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20detecting%20past-due%20invoices%20and%20automatically%20drafting%20a%20personalized%20reminder%20note.%20After%20a%20business%20owner%20approves%20the%20note's%20language%20and%20sends%20it%20out%2C%20they%20are%20paid%2C%20on%20average%2C%20five%20days%20sooner%20than%20with%20a%20human-only%20process%2C%20Intuit%20Assist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20Inuit%20Assist%20takes%20action%2C%20humans%20have%20the%20final%20say.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20have%20the%20right%20human-automation%20interaction%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashok%20Srivastava%2C%20Intuit's%20chief%20data%20officer%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntuit%20has%20embraced%20a%20robust%20AI-training%20program%2C%20focused%20on%20responsible%20AI%20and%20what%20the%20technology%20can%20and%20cannot%20do%2C%20and%20built%20a%20%26quot%3Bsandbox%26quot%3B%20called%20GenStudio%20that%20allows%20employees%20to%20interact%20with%20large%20language%20models%20in%20a%20secure%20environment.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20developed%20educational%20programs%20tailored%20to%20senior%20executives%2C%20directors%2C%20and%20engineers.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20pervasive%20across%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Srivastava%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsana%2C%20which%20makes%20work-management%20software%2C%20launched%20AI%20agents%20in%20October%2C%20focusing%20on%20a%20few%20functions%2C%20including%20marketing%2C%20IT%2C%20HR%2C%20and%20research%20and%20development.%20Rather%20than%20track%20a%20specific%20number%20of%20actions%20that%20agentic%20AI%20takes%20over%2C%20Asana%20monitors%20the%20types%20of%20work%20that%20can%20be%20automated%2C%20eliminating%20the%20drudgery%20of%20busy%20work%20to%20allow%20employees%20to%20focus%20on%20more%20complex%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20which%20tasks%20AI%20systems%20get%20wrong%20compared%20with%20people.%20In%20cybersecurity%2C%20human%20errors%20tend%20to%20occur%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20when%20workers%20are%20tired%20after%20a%20long%20shift.%20AI%20doesn't%20get%20tired%2C%20but%20it%20is%20susceptible%20to%20hallucinations%20%E2%80%94%20or%20when%20an%20AI%20model%20generates%20a%20response%20that%20is%20misleading%20or%20false%20information%20but%20nonetheless%20presents%20it%20as%20fact.%20For%20example%2C%20Asana's%20AI%20agent%20might%20respond%20to%20certain%20questions%20by%20suggesting%20tasks%20that%20are%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20nonexistent%20to%20a%20particular%20workflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kinds%20of%20errors%20we%20see%20are%20different%2C%20so%20the%20way%20we%20fix%20them%20needs%20to%20be%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Asana's%20chief%20information%20security%20officer%2C%20Sean%20Cassidy%2C%20said.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20conducts%20automated%20tests%20to%20detect%20hallucinations%20and%20improve%20the%20product%20when%20they%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20AI%20agents%20to%20create%20a%20compelling%20return%20on%20investment%20for%20the%20companies%20that%20implement%20them%2C%20Deloitte's%20Rowan%20said%2C%20workers%20should%20be%20tasked%20with%20frequently%20checking%20on%20simple%20automated%20tasks%20before%20any%20agentic%20AI%20actions%20are%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20businesses%20want%20to%20see%20big%20returns%20on%20their%20agentic%20AI%20investme