20tariffs%20on%20Canada%2C%20a%20close%20ally%20and%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20the%20United%20States%20has%20launched%20a%20trade%20war%20against%20Canada.%20Its%20closest%20partner%20and%20ally%2C%20its%20closest%20friend%26quot%3B%2C%20Trudeau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20US%20tariffs%2C%20Canada%20will%20implement%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20%24155%20billion%20worth%20of%20American%20goods%2C%20starting%20with%20%2430%20billion%20worth%20of%20goods%20immediately%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20%24125%20billion%20worth%20of%20goods%20in%2021%20days.%20Trudeau%20also%20announced%20plans%20to%20challenge%20US's%20%26quot%3Billegal%20actions%26quot%3B%20or%20tariffs%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%2C%20citing%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20free%20trade%20agreement%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20moment%20U.S.%20tariffs%20came%20into%20effect%20this%20morning%2C%20so%20did%20the%20Canadian%20response.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCanada%20will%20be%20implementing%2025%25%20tariffs%20against%20%24155%20billion%20of%20American%20products.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnStarting%20with%20%2430%20billion%20worth%20of%20goods%20immediately%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20%24125%20billion%20in%2021%20days'%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Justin%20Trudeau%20(%40JustinTrudeau)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJustinTrudeau%2Fstatus%2F1896964152822050953%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20addressed%20the%20American%20public%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20tariffs%20will%20lead%20to%20inflation%20and%20harm%20American%20jobs%2C%20particularly%20in%20workplaces%20that%20rely%20on%20materials%20or%20consumers%20from%20Canada.%20He%20urged%20Trump%20to%20reconsider%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20should%20work%20together%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bprosperity%20for%20North%20Americans%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20chosen%20to%20sabotage%20their%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20adds.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20absolutely%20no%20justification%20or%20need%20for%20these%20tariffs%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20government%20has%20also%20announced%20measures%20to%20support%20Canadians%20affected%20by%20the%20trade%20war%2C%20including%20expanding%20support%20for%20those%20who%20lose%20their%20jobs%20and%20helping%20businesses%20stay%20afloat.%20Trudeau%20assured%20Canadians%20that%20the%20government%20will%20%26quot%3Brelentlessly%20fight%26quot%3B%20to%20protect%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20addressed%20the%20fentanyl%20issue%20and%20insisted%20that%20Trump's%20claim%20that%20Canada%20is%20unwilling%20to%20fight%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Btotally%20false%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20also%20said%20that%20Trump%20wants%20to%20see%20a%20total%20collapse%20of%20the%20Canadian%20economy%20just%20so%20that%20it%20will%20become%20easier%20to%20annex%20Canada%2C%20while%20reiterating%20that%20that%20will%20never%20happen%20and%20%26quot%3BCanada%20will%20never%20be%20the%2051st%20state%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%2C%20who%20is%20the%20outgoing%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Canada%20has%20been%20in%20power%20since%202015%20and%20is%20due%20to%20be%20replaced%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20governing%20Liberal%20Party%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20Canadians%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20fight%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20win.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741110720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F6954ep_trudeau-reuters_625x300_04_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjustin-trudeau-slaps-25-tariffs-on-us-calls-donald-tr