n%20filed%20by%20child%20activist%20Ridhima%20Pandey%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20carbon%20emission%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20climate%20change%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20existential%20global%20predicament%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20PS%20Narasimha%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20it%20had%20ramifications%20that%20go%20beyond%20environmental%20degradation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEscalating%20temperatures%2C%20erratic%20weather%20patterns%2C%20and%20the%20proliferation%20of%20extreme%20climatic%20events%20such%20as%20floods%2C%20droughts%2C%20and%20heatwaves%20not%20only%20imperil%20ecosystems%20but%20also%20disrupt%20human%20life%2C%20livelihoods%20and%20socio-economic%20structures.%20The%20economic%20ramifications%20are%20equally%20profound%2C%20as%20climate%20change%20exacerbates%20vulnerabilities%20to%20public%20health%2C%20low%20per%20acre%20yield%20leading%20to%20declining%20agricultural%20productivity%20and%20increase%20in%20energy%20consumption%20amongst%20many%20other%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20socio-economic%20repercussions%20of%20this%20are%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20acute%20in%20fast%20developing%20nations%20like%20India%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20added%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20addressing%20climate%20change%20is%20crucial%20to%20economic%20resilience%2C%20social%20justice%2C%20and%20sustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20advised%20a%20re-assessment%20of%20the%20existing%20laws%20protecting%20environment%20-%20including%20the%20Environment%20Protection%20Act%2C%20and%20the%201981%20law%20on%20control%20of%20air%20pollution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20another%20petition%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20has%20directed%20all%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20to%20form%20expert%20committee%20to%20prepare%20a%20la