ing%20Programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20in%20question%20was%20announced%20on%20February%2011%20and%20includes%20nearly%2010%2C000%20sq%20km%20within%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mannar%20Marine%20Biosphere%20Reserve%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20marine%20national%20park%20that%20is%20spread%20over%20560%20sq%20km.%20The%20dugong%20reserve%20is%20spread%20over%20448%20sq%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDMK%20vs%20BJP%20War%20Continues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin's%20letter%20comes%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20DMK%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20centre%20lock%20horns%20over%20two%20contentious%20issues%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20the%20allegation%20of%20'Hindi%20imposition'%2C%20that%20the%20centre%2C%20through%20its%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20is%20forcing%20Tamil%20students%20to%20learn%20Hindi.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20long%20been%20suspicious%20of%20having%20the%20language%20foisted%20upon%20it%2C%20and%20has%20twice%20before%20launched%20fierce%20protests%20on%20this%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindi-imposition-row-mk-stalin-tamil-nadu-language-war-hindi-destroyed-25-north-indian-languages-mk-stalin-targets-centre-7805575%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSaying%20Silly%20Things%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20On%20Stalin's%20%26quot%3BHindi%20Destroyed%2025...%26quot%3B%20Jab%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20has%20said%20there%20is%20no%20plan%20to%20'impose'%20Hindi%2C%20but%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20DMK%20for%20linking%20central%20funds%20to%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelimitation-exercise-2026-lok-sabha-election-2029-mk-stalin-hindi-imposition-tamil-nadu-language-war-