sed%20for%20the%20son%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20You%20also%20were%20present%20on%20the%20occasion...%20Did%20your%20father%20not%20use%20abusive%20words%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%3F%20Stand%20up%20and%20deny%20it%20if%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20broke%20out%20in%20a%20storm%20of%20protest%2C%20Mr%20Choudhury%20hit%20back.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20your%20father%20say%3F%20He%20looted%20Bihar.%20He%20looted%20the%20poor.%20He%20robbed%20the%20whole%20state%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20to%20jail.%20Lalu%20Prasad%20sent%20me%20to%20jail.%20It%20was%20only%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar...%26quot%3B%20--%20he%20had%20only%20got%20that%20far%20when%20Mr%20Yadav%20cut%20across%3A%20%26quot%3BFrom%20which%20party%20did%20you%20win%20the%20last%20time%3F%20It%20was%20our%20party.%20After%20that%20you%20are%20fated%20to%20lose%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20consider%20yourself%20a%20king%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chaudhury%20scoffed.%20%26quot%3BAt%20least%20I%20have%20not%20used%20any%20abusive%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20shot%20back.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamrat%20Chaudhary%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20government%20headed%20by%20Rabri%20Devi%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav%20when%20he%20went%20to%20jail%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20fodder%20scam.%20He%20remained%20with%20the%20RJD%20even%20after%20it%20lost%20power%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20he%20became%20part%20of%20a%20rebel%20faction%20and%20joined%20the%20JD(U)%20government%20headed%20by%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20recognised%20his%20potential%20as%20a%20fiery%20speaker%20and%20the%20face%20of%20the%20prominent%20Koeri%20caste.%20His%20rise%20in%20the%20party%20has%20been%20meteoric%20--%20%C2%A0vice-president%20of%20the%20state%20unit%2C%20a%2